<exercise id="fs-idm207197696">
<problem id="fs-idm216317136">
<para id="fs-idm202688416"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68110"/>Explain the difference between prime costs and conversion costs.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm219730816">
<para id="fs-idm218214048">Answers will vary but should include that prime costs are the direct material and direct labor costs, and conversion costs are direct labor and general factory overhead combined.</para>
</solution>
